name: Janus Greejatus
Lore: 'Imperial council member. Very cruel at heart. Has lusted for power his entire life. Predictable and controllable.',
Text: 'Deploys -3 to Emperor''s site. When with Emperor at a battleground site, adds 1 to your Force drains here. Once per turn, you may use 1 Force to place a card from hand to bottom of Used Pile and draw top card of Reserve Deck. Immune to attrition < 3.',
